'''散布區'''這個名詞是指單一[[隕石|隕石]]墬落在地面上所分散的區域<ref>''Introduction to Planetary Science: The Geological Perspective''. Gunter Faure, Teresa M. Mensing. Springer, 2007. [http://books.google.it/books?id=U4FZp6f6q6MC&pg=PA118 page 118] {{Wayback|url=http://books.google.it/books?id=U4FZp6f6q6MC&pg=PA118 |date=20120304014951 }}</ref>，它也經常用於[[玻璃隕石|似曜石]]這種大型的隕石撞擊<ref>''Tektites in the geological record: showers of glass from the sky''. Gerald Joseph Home McCall. Geological Society of London, 2001. [http://books.google.it/books?id=1mywn15XjFIC&pg=PA10 page 10] {{Wayback|url=http://books.google.it/books?id=1mywn15XjFIC&pg=PA10 |date=20120304015000 }}</ref>。
